# App Landing Page

🚀 **Welcome to the App Landing Page Project!**

This is a simple and modern landing page designed for promoting mobile or desktop applications. The design is responsive, clean, and easy to customize.

## 📄 Project Contents
- `landing.html`: The main landing page file with inline CSS styling.

## 🌐 Live Demo
Once deployed, your site will be available at:
```
https://your-username.github.io/app-landing-page/
```

## 🚀 How to Use
1. Clone or download this repository.
2. Open `landing.html` in your browser.
3. Edit the file to customize the content, colors, links, and images.

## 🚀 Deployment on GitHub Pages
1. Go to your repository's **Settings**.
2. Navigate to **Pages** in the sidebar.
3. Select **Branch: main** and **/ (root)**.
4. Click **Save**.
5. Your page will be live at the provided URL.

## 🛠️ Customization
- **Title**: Change the `<title>` tag in the HTML.
- **Text Content**: Edit the `<h1>`, `<p>`, and button label.
- **Download Link**: Replace `href="#"` with your app's download link.
- **Image**: Update the image URL to show your app preview.

## 📧 Contact
For any questions or customization requests, feel free to contact me.

---

Enjoy your new landing page! 🎉
